description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP Talks to Sunday Night Football's Cris Collinsworth who will be on the call for the big game. Mike Irvin joins the boys in-studio and brings all the energy. Rich Eisen discusses shoulder position in group pictures. And Barry Sanders tells us where he would have gone to school if he didn't commit to Oklahoma State.
